                        <ul>
                            <li>Converting wooden pallets into composters and benches for community and home use.</li>
                            <li>Building small green houses and cold frames to grow local vegetables.</li>
                            <li>Repurposing old tires to create Christmas decorations for the village squares and comfortable tables and chairs for homes.</li>
                            <li>Creating candles and decorations out of recycled materials that are sold or given as gifts.</li>
                            <li>Initiating other community environmentally-friendly projects, including environmentally green bus-and-bicycle stops, greening school environments.</li>
